chapters.title: According to Jesus why His people are destroyed Hosea 4:6
According to Paul what is Satan transformed into? [2 Corinthians 11:14]
Corinthians 11:14] And no marvel; for Satan himself is transformed into an angel of light.
How did the angels come into existence? Colossians 1:14-17
THE TYPES AND RANKS OF ANGELS
What did an angel refuse to allow the apostle John to do to him? [Rev. 22:8-9, Colossians 2:18]
For in the resurrection they neither marry, nor are given in marriage, but are as the angels of God in heaven
